Get GPR CSR and FP registers from kvm by KVM_GET_ONE_REG ioctl.

Signed-off-by: Yifei Jiang <jiangyifei@huawei.com>
Signed-off-by: Yipeng Yin <yinyipeng1@huawei.com>
---
